    "questionText": "You are documenting the specifications for a main sub-feed cable. Explain how the cable's physical dimensions (length and cross-sectional area) and its material property (resistivity) dictate the final resistance of the conductor. Your explanation must include the correct SI units and symbols for all four quantities mentioned.",
